      • source

        public String source()
        The source location of a copy command. If "copying to" a Device, then the source represents a file resource that is present on the local environment. If "copying from" a Device, then this value represents the file location on the Device.
        Returns:
        The path representing the CopyInput source

      • destination

        public String destination()
        The destination of a copy command. If "copying to" a Device, then the destination represents the file location that will manifest on the Device. If "copying from" a Device, then the destination represents a file location in the local environment.
        Returns:
        The path representing the CopyInput destination
